<L>__{int gus's basement later}
<A>__{hazel descends the steps. she hears an ungodly moan before she sees anyone. what has she gotten herself into? gus appears at the base.}
<C>__{gus}
<P>__{(calling to isaac)}
<D>__{isaac, hazel from support group is coming downstairs.}
