<C>__{gus}
<D>__{a gentle reminder: isaac is in the midst of a psychotic episode.}
<P>__{(hazel nods)}
<D>__{you look nice, by the way.}
<A>__{hazel blushes, follows gus into the room to find isaac sitting upside down in a gaming chair. tears are flowing down his reddened cheeks. empty soda cans and bags of junk food lie around him.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{how ya doing isaac?}
<A>__{again, no response. hazel looks to gus for an explanation.}
<C>__{gus}
<D>__{seems isaac and monica are no longer a going concern.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{oh i'm sorry.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{do you want to talk about it?}
<A>__{isaac starts to sob again.}
<C>__{gus}
<D>__{he just wants to cry and play video games.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{fair enough.}
<C>__{gus}
<D>__{it doesn't hurt to talk to him, however. if you have any sage words of feminine advice...}
